						<summary>

						<p>Slab setup behind the Hanumān temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Nūrmaḍi Trailōkyamalla [Sōmēśvara IV] 1154 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This fragment belonging to the reign period of Chālukya nūrmaḍi Traiḷōkyamalladēva refers to the <hi rend="italic">prabhu</hi> of Baḷḷaniṭṭage.</p>						

						<p>It is dated in the 4th regnal year (of the king) Bhava, Pushya, śu. 10. Thursday, <hi rend="italic">uttarāyaṇa</hi> <hi rend="italic">saṁkrānti.</hi> It corresponds to 1154 A.D., December 16. But there was no saṁkrānti on that day.</p>						

						</summary>
